<div class="jumbotron">
    <div class="container-welcome">
        <h1>CONNECT<br>ENJOY<br>PROGRESS</h1>
    </div>
</div>
<main class="main home-sections">
    <article class='row'>
        <div class='col-md-7 col-md-offset-3'>
            <p id='intro'>We have some services your going to love. At your convenience, view our offerings, schedule appointment or reach out, we'd love to hear from you. Sure were awesome apart but we get more done together.</p>
        </div>
    </article>
    <section>
        <div class="container" id="cnt1">
            <div class="row feature">
                <div class="col-md-4 link-card">
                    <div>
                        <%= image_tag "sunrise.jpg", alt: "sunrise", class: "img-circle img-thumbnail" %>
                        <h2>Services</h2>
                        <p>
                            An indepth look at our offerings.  From life changing rehabilitation to serious rest and relaxation. Treat yourself or make a friends day.
                        </p>
                        <%= button_to "See Menu", services_path, :method => "get", class:"btn btn-success lower"%>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-4 link-card">
                    <div>
                        <%= image_tag "mountain-river.jpg", alt:"Texto Alternativo", class:"img-circle img-thumbnail" %>
                        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                        <p>This website was created for your convenience. Here is a list of the most frequently asked question. If your looking to talk to a real person, please call the toll free line at the bottom of the page.You got questions we got answer.
                        <%= button_to "FAQ", about_path, :method => "get", class:"btn btn-success lower"%>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-4 link-card">
                    <div>
                        <%= image_tag "scenic2.jpg", alt:"Texto Alternativo", class:"img-circle img-thumbnail"%>
                        <% if current_user %>
                        <h2>
                            Welcome back.</h2>
                        <p>
                            Please click the button if you'd like to review your history and other goodies.</p>
                        <%= button_to "Profile View", user_path(current_user), :method => "get", class: "btn btn-success"  %>
                    <% else %>
                        <h2>Create A free account</h2>
                        <p>
                            If you wont settle for mediocre and want us available at your leisure. Please, create an account and
                            streamline your rest and relaxation.
                        </p>
                        <%= button_to "Join the Fun!", new_user_path, :method => "get", class: "btn btn-lg btn-success" %>
                        <% end %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <section id="carousel-testimonials" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
            <!-- Indicators -->
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                <li data-target="#carousel-testimonials" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                <li data-target="#carousel-testimonials" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                <li data-target="#carousel-testimonials" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                <li data-target="#carousel-testimonials" data-slide-to="3"></li>
            </ol>

            <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
            <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
                <div class="item active">
                    <%= image_tag "writing.jpeg", alt:"testimonial"%>
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <p>Treat Yourself!!!.
                        </p>
                        <cite>Aziz Ansari</cite>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <%= image_tag "writing2.jpeg", alt:"testimonial" %>
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <p> I repeatedly bought groupons but couldn't get booked for weeks. This website makes it easy to get in touch.
                        </p>
                        <cite>Recovering Grouponer</cite>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <%= image_tag "writingFancy.jpeg", alt:"testimonial" %>
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <p>I good friend got bought me a gift certificate. I scheduled an appointment and got an awesome Thai massage.
                        </p>
                        <cite>Mr literal</cite>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                    <%= image_tag "writing1.jpeg", alt:"testimonial"%>
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <p>Doctor said I need a backiotomy, I didn't know what to do until I found this site I can easily see his availability and check in with questions or appointments.
                        </p>
                        <cite>Sir Smoke-alot -Half Baked</cite>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Controls -->
            <a class="left carousel-control" href="#carousel-testimonials" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="right carousel-control" href="#carousel-testimonials" role="button" data-slide="next">
                <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>
